### FlareLog API 接口测试
### 使用前请先配置 .vscode/settings.json 中的 rest-client 插件的 host 和 apiKey 变量
### VS Code 推荐安装 REST Client 插件, JetBrains IDE 原生支持

### ============================================================
### 服务信息 (无需认证)
### ============================================================

### 获取服务信息
GET {{host}}/

### ============================================================
### 日志写入
### ============================================================

### 接收单条日志 - 最简写法 (只填必填字段)
POST {{host}}/api/logs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

{
  "service": "test-service",
  "message": "Hello from FlareLog"
}

### 接收单条日志 - 完整字段
POST {{host}}/api/logs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

{
  "level": "error",
  "service": "api-gateway",
  "message": "Connection timeout to database",
  "timestamp": "2025-04-30T10:00:00.000Z",
  "trace_id": "trace-abc-123",
  "metadata": {
    "host": "db-primary",
    "port": 5432,
    "retry_count": 3
  }
}

### 接收单条日志 - 使用 X-API-Key 认证
POST {{host}}/api/logs
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "level": "warn",
  "service": "auth-service",
  "message": "Rate limit approaching for user"
}

### 接收单条日志 - debug 级别
POST {{host}}/api/logs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

{
  "level": "debug",
  "service": "worker-pool",
  "message": "Worker spawned, idle connections: 12",
  "trace_id": "req-004"
}

### 接收单条日志 - 带 metadata
POST {{host}}/api/logs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

{
  "level": "info",
  "service": "payment-service",
  "message": "Order created successfully",
  "metadata": {
    "order_id": "ORD-20250430-001",
    "amount": 99.9,
    "currency": "CNY"
  }
}

### 批量接收日志
POST {{host}}/api/logs/batch
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

{
  "logs": [
    {
      "level": "info",
      "service": "auth-service",
      "message": "User login successful",
      "trace_id": "req-001"
    },
    {
      "level": "warn",
      "service": "auth-service",
      "message": "Rate limit approaching",
      "trace_id": "req-001"
    },
    {
      "level": "error",
      "service": "db-service",
      "message": "Query execution failed",
      "trace_id": "req-002",
      "metadata": {
        "query": "SELECT * FROM users WHERE id = ?",
        "error_code": "SQLITE_BUSY"
      }
    }
  ]
}

### ============================================================
### 日志查询
### ============================================================

### 查询所有日志 (默认: 每页50条, 按 timestamp 降序)
GET {{host}}/api/logs
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### 按 level 过滤
GET {{host}}/api/logs?level=error
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### 按 levels 多选过滤 (逗号分隔)
GET {{host}}/api/logs?levels=error,warn
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### 按 service 过滤
GET {{host}}/api/logs?service=api-gateway
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### 按 trace_id 过滤
GET {{host}}/api/logs?trace_id=trace-abc-123
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### 按 message 模糊搜索
GET {{host}}/api/logs?message=timeout
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### 按时间范围过滤
GET {{host}}/api/logs?start_time=2025-04-30T00:00:00.000Z&end_time=2025-04-30T23:59:59.999Z
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### 自定义分页 (每页10条, 偏移20)
GET {{host}}/api/logs?limit=10&offset=20
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### 按 created_at 升序排序
GET {{host}}/api/logs?sort=created_at&order=asc
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### 复合查询: level + service + 时间范围 + 分页
GET {{host}}/api/logs?level=error&service=api-gateway&start_time=2025-04-01T00:00:00.000Z&limit=20&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### 根据 ID 查询单条日志
GET {{host}}/api/logs/1
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### ============================================================
### 日志删除
### ============================================================

### 删除单条日志
DELETE {{host}}/api/logs/1
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### 按 service 批量删除
DELETE {{host}}/api/logs?service=test-service
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### 按时间范围批量删除 (删除指定时间之前的日志)
DELETE {{host}}/api/logs?before=2025-04-01T00:00:00.000Z
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### 按 service + 时间范围批量删除 (AND 条件)
DELETE {{host}}/api/logs?service=api-gateway&before=2025-04-30T00:00:00.000Z
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### ============================================================
### 错误场景测试
### ============================================================

### 无认证 - 应返回 401
POST {{host}}/api/logs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "service": "test",
  "message": "This should fail"
}

### 错误的 API Key - 应返回 401
POST {{host}}/api/logs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer wrong-key

{
  "service": "test",
  "message": "This should fail"
}

### 缺少必填字段 service - 应返回 400
POST {{host}}/api/logs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

{
  "message": "Missing service field"
}

### 缺少必填字段 message - 应返回 400
POST {{host}}/api/logs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

{
  "service": "test-service"
}

### 无效的 level - 应降级为 info 而非报错 (level 不合法时自动降级)
POST {{host}}/api/logs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

{
  "level": "critical",
  "service": "test-service",
  "message": "Invalid level will be downgraded to info"
}

### 无效的 timestamp - 应返回 400
POST {{host}}/api/logs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

{
  "service": "test-service",
  "message": "Bad timestamp",
  "timestamp": "not-a-date"
}

### 空的批量日志数组 - 应返回 400
POST {{host}}/api/logs/batch
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

{
  "logs": []
}

### 批量日志中某条校验失败 - 应返回 400 并指出索引
POST {{host}}/api/logs/batch
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

{
  "logs": [
    {
      "service": "ok-service",
      "message": "This one is fine"
    },
    {
      "message": "Missing service in this entry"
    }
  ]
}

### 批量删除不提供参数 - 应返回 400
DELETE {{host}}/api/logs
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### 查询不存在的日志 ID - 应返回 404
GET {{host}}/api/logs/999999
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### 删除不存在的日志 ID - 应返回 404
DELETE {{host}}/api/logs/999999
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### 查询时传入无效 level - 应返回 400
GET {{host}}/api/logs?level=unknown
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### 查询时传入无效 sort 字段 - 应返回 400
GET {{host}}/api/logs?sort=invalid_field
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### 非 JSON Content-Type - 应返回 415
POST {{host}}/api/logs
Content-Type: text/plain
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

this is not json
